'''MeraStel''' was a large company based in the [[Darpa sector/Legends|Darpa sector]]. It grew to its climax during the height of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], when the company hired nonhumans for minimum wage. During the attacks of the [[Faceless]] on Imperial operations on [[Esseles/Legends|Esseles]], the nonhumans began to strike because of the Empire's anti-alien bias. These strikes would render MeraStel useless and dependent on a droid workforce until negotiations between [[Kanno Sebak]] and [[Hall President]] [[Cambira Ralle]] ended the strike.

